<!-- Drawer — spec card render
     Source spec: ds-architect-agent/children/components/overlays.md#drawer -->
<div class="dst-component-card">
  <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-2">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Drawer</h3>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono">3 variants · 4 sizes · 4 states</p>
  </div>
  <p class="dst-component-intro">Side-anchored panel. Used for secondary navigation (mobile sidebar), filters, contextual sub-views.</p>

  <div class="dst-spec-row">
    <span class="dst-spec-label">Variants</span>
    <div class="dst-spec-values">
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-variant">left · mobile primary nav</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-variant">right · filters / details</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-variant">bottom · mobile sheet</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dst-spec-row">
    <span class="dst-spec-label">Sizes</span>
    <div class="dst-spec-values">
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-size">sm · 280px</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-size">md · 360px</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-size">lg · 480px</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-size">full · 100%</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dst-spec-row">
    <span class="dst-spec-label">States</span>
    <div class="dst-spec-values">
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">closed</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">opening</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">open</span>
      <span class="dst-spec-pill dst-pill-state">closing</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="dst-spec-note"><strong>Behavior:</strong> same scrim / escape / focus rules as modal. Bottom-anchored drawer doesn't trap focus on tablets where it doesn't fully cover the screen. <strong>Animation:</strong> slide in from anchor edge (decelerate, normal); slide out (accelerate, fast).</div>
</div>
